      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about getting drunk. i mean like just a small glass of wine, maybe 5oz? it feels like it would just help me get into that relaxed state faster so the medicine can actually do its job. won't a tiny amount just make it more effective rather than actually being dangerous?",
